name: HTTPCookiePropertyKey
desc: Constants that define the supported keys in a cookie attributes dictionary.

items.name: static let comment: HTTPCookiePropertyKey
items.desc: An NSString object containing the comment for the cookie.

items.name: static let commentURL: HTTPCookiePropertyKey
items.desc: An NSURL object or NSString object containing the comment URL for the cookie.

items.name: static let discard: HTTPCookiePropertyKey
items.desc: An NSString object stating whether the cookie should be discarded at the end of the session.

items.name: static let domain: HTTPCookiePropertyKey
items.desc: An NSString object containing the domain for the cookie.

items.name: static let expires: HTTPCookiePropertyKey
items.desc: An NSDate object or NSString object specifying the expiration date for the cookie.

items.name: static let maximumAge: HTTPCookiePropertyKey
items.desc: An NSString object containing an integer value stating how long in seconds the cookie should be kept, at most.

items.name: static let name: HTTPCookiePropertyKey
items.desc: An NSString object containing the name of the cookie (required).

items.name: static let originURL: HTTPCookiePropertyKey
items.desc: An NSURL or NSString object containing the URL that set this cookie.

items.name: static let path: HTTPCookiePropertyKey
items.desc: An NSString object containing the path for the cookie.

items.name: static let port: HTTPCookiePropertyKey
items.desc: An NSString object containing comma-separated integer values specifying the ports for the cookie.

items.name: static let sameSitePolicy: HTTPCookiePropertyKey
items.desc: A string indicating the same-site policy for the cookie.

items.name: static let secure: HTTPCookiePropertyKey
items.desc: An NSString object indicating that the cookie should be transmitted only over secure channels.

items.name: static let value: HTTPCookiePropertyKey
items.desc: An NSString object containing the value of the cookie.

items.name: static let version: HTTPCookiePropertyKey
items.desc: An NSString object that specifies the version of the cookie.

items.name: init(String)
items.desc: Creates an HTTP cookie property key using the given string.

items.name: init(rawValue: String)
items.desc: Creates an HTTP cookie property key using the given string.
